parameter.desc:
Current state of write protection mode of SLCR:
0 - Registers are writeable;
1 - Registers are not writeable. Any attempted writes are ignored, but reads will complete as normal.

When the APU watchdog timer 0 goes off, the SLCR can control whether the whole system is reboot or just the ARM core who's WDT went off will be reset.
0 - reset Pele;
1 - reset ARM core
